Description of problem:
By default keybinding for lock screen Ctrl+Alt+L doesn't work. Changing it for something like Ctrl+<letter> or Alt+<letter> or Ctrl+Alt+<letter> doesn't work too. But binding like Ctrl+Space, Alt+Space, Ctrl+Alt+Space works fine.
Also Ctrl+Alt+D for showing desktop - also works fine. But the same binding for lock screen doesn't work.

Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):
mate-screensaver-1.10.1-1.fc22.x86_64


How reproducible:


Steps to Reproduce:
